ceop.labelTxt: What type of Airspace do you believe are vital to protect (Choose your 2nd priority)?
ceop.ans1: All Airport runways and approach paths
ceop.ans2: Airspace near airports (and specifically the portions of the airspace above the "LAANC altitudes")
ceop.ans3: Security sensitive airspace restrictions (Flight Restricted, FR)
ceop.ans4: Approach/departure paths of Class B and C airports
ceop.ans5: Restricted or Special Use Airspace (DoD etc) TFRs under 14 CFR 99.7 & 91 (ANY)
